OL,3,CDriver caught by police trimming beard
OL,4,Con motorway
OL,6,FA driver has been filmed trimming his
OL,7,Fbeard while travelling at speed on a
OL,8,Fmotorway.
OL,10,FIn footage released by South Yorkshire
OL,11,FPolice, the man is seen using clippers
OL,12,Fto groom his facial hair, at times
OL,13,Fwith neither hand on the wheel.
OL,15,FThe video was taken from a National
OL,16,FHighways lorry, which was on patrol on
OL,17,Fthe M1, M18 and A1 over five days in
OL,18,FJuly.
