OL,6,FPolice stopped 240 drivers for
OL,7,Foffences including using a mobile
OL,8,Fphone, not wearing a seatbelt, and
OL,9,Fdriving without due care and attention.
OL,11,FOne vehicle was pictured carrying
OL,12,Flivestock on a trailer with one bird
OL,13,Fout of its cage.
OL,15,FThirty-one drivers were dealt with for
OL,16,Fstopping on the hard shoulder, two
OL,17,Fwere caught speeding and three were
OL,18,Fseen driving through a red X.
