OL,4,Con motorway
OL,6,FRoads policing inspector Matt Collings
OL,7,Fsaid: "Enforcing against those who
OL,8,Fpose a risk on our roads is daily
OL,9,Fbusiness for officers and we're always
OL,10,Fkeen to make the most of being
OL,11,Fprovided the cab by National Highways
OL,12,Fto support our work.
OL,14,F"We last carried this operation out in
OL,15,FMay, just under three months ago, and
OL,16,Fsadly within that short space of time
OL,17,Fa further eight people have lost their
OL,18,Flives on South Yorkshire's roads.
